Technical Analysis
 • History repeats itself
Two major factors to be analysed in technical analysis are price and volume.

 • Analysis of price: there are 4 major parameters to be analysed for price Open, High, Low and Close (OHLC)

 • Trend: when all the prices are plotted on a graph, we can see a general direction of the price movement and that is known as trend. Trend comprises of upmoves and downmoves.

 • Analysis of volume: Number of shares which traded during the day 